! A data file for diablo.  This is a generic, easy method of data
! input, as long as you don't change the number of comment lines.
! Note that the grid size is defined in the file grid_def.
!   FLAVOR        VERSION    
    'Front'        2.0        
!   USE_MPI       USE_LES   (note, also change these flags in Makefile):
    .TRUE.       .TRUE.               
! Parameters:     NU,          BETA,       LX,       LY,     LZ
                  0.000001      1.0       16000.0    1000.0   16000.0 
! Vertical viscosity scale factor NU_V_SCALE (NU_V=NU*NU_V_SCALE)
                  1.0  
! Method:     NUM_PER_DIR, CREATE_NEW_FLOW
                  2            .TRUE.        
! Time March:  N_TIME_STEPS, TIME_LIMIT, DELTA_T, RESET_TIME, VARIABLE_DT, CFL, UPDATE_DT
                 600000        500000       0.1      .FALSE.      .TRUE.     0.5      1
! I/O:         VERBOSITY, SAVE_FLOW_INT, SAVE_STATS_INT,  MOVIE
                   4          200            200          .TRUE. 
! Here include 6*N_TH lines, see below for format
!         CREATE_FLOW_TH(1)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
!         FILTER_TH(1)         FILTER_INT(1)     (If and how often to filter)
               .FALSE.              10
!         RI_TAU(1)          PR(1)      
             1.0              1.0        
!         CREATE_FLOW_TH(2)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
!         FILTER_TH(2)         FILTER_INT(2)     (If and how often to filter)
               .FALSE.              10
!         RI_TAU(2)          PR(2)
                0.0              1.0
!         CREATE_FLOW_TH(3)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
!         FILTER_TH(3)         FILTER_INT(3)     (If and how often to filter)
               .FALSE.              10
!         RI_TAU(3)          PR(3)
                0.0              1.0

! When including scalar advection, include 6 lines like the following for each scalar

!         CREATE_FLOW_TH(1)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
!         FILTER_TH(1)         FILTER_INT(1)     (If and how often to filter)
               .TRUE.                10
!         RI_TAU(1)      PR(1)       BACKGROUND_TH(N)
             0.0             1.0          .FALSE.
!         CREATE_FLOW_TH(2)  Create new field or Read from DIABLO_TH.START
               .TRUE.
!         FILTER_TH(2)         FILTER_INT(2)     (If and how often to filter)
               .TRUE.                10
!         RI_TAU(2)      PR(2)       BACKGROUND_TH(N)
                0.0             1.0          .FALSE.
